
'''Monique Mukaruliza''' ni umunyapolitiki [[Rwanda|w'umunyarwandakazi]] ukora nk'umujyanama wa minisiteri y’ububanyi n’amahanga n’ubufatanye mpuzamahanga (MINAFETT) mu [[Rwanda]] . <ref>https://en.igihe.com/news/article/amb-mukaruliza-appointed-strategic-advisor-in-minafett</ref>

== Umwuga ==
Mbere yuko ahabwa inshingano, Mukaruliza yagizwe uwahoze ari Ambasaderi w'u [[Rwanda]] muri [[Zambiya]] . <ref>https://www.icnl.org/wp-content/uploads/CabinetCom.pdf</ref> <ref>https://umuryango.rw/index.php?page=print&id_article=29265</ref> Yabaye umuyobozi w'umujyi wa [[Kigali]] hagati ya 2016 na 2017, umuyobozi wa gatatu w’umugore kuva mu 1996. <ref>https://www.newtimes.co.rw/section/read/197529</ref> <ref>https://theprepaideconomy.com/post/140213093278/monique-mukaruliza-is-new-kigali-city-mayor</ref> Yabaye umuyobozi wa [[Ishyaka FPR-Inkotanyi|FPR]] mu [[Kigali|Mujyi wa Kigali]] <ref>https://rpfinkotanyi.rw/index.php?id=187&tx_news_pi1%5Bnews%5D=301&tx_news_pi1%5Bcontroller%5D=News&tx_news_pi1%5Baction%5D=detail&cHash=f2d811e2e6c17c72cdd56ebaec161101</ref> kandi yabaye Minisitiri wa mbere [[Umuryango w’Ibihugu by’Iburasirazuba bw’Afurika|w’umuryango w’ibihugu bya Afurika y'Iburasirazuba]] (MINEAC). <ref>http://repository.eac.int/bitstream/handle/11671/365/397-three-eala-members-sworn-in-.pdf?sequence=1&isAllowed=y</ref> <ref>https://www.newtimes.co.rw/section/read/67580</ref> Mukaruliza yatangiye imirimo nka minisitiri wa MINEAC mu 2008 kugeza ku ya 25 Gashyantare 2013. <ref>https://www.eala.org/index.php/media/view/rwandas-eac-minister-sworn-in-as-eala-member</ref> <ref>http://www.mfa.gov.sg/Newsroom/Press-Statements-Transcripts-and-Photos/2008/03/MFA-Press-Statement-Call-On-Rwanda-President-Paul-Kagame-by-Senior-Minister-Of-State-For-Foreign-Aff</ref> Mbere yuko ajya muri MINEAC, Mukaruliza yari ahagarariye Umuryango w’ubumwe bw’Afurika muri [[Sudani]] kandi yabaye umuyobozi wungirije wa komisiyo ya AU muri Sudani hagati ya 2005 na 2008. '''<ref>https://reliefweb.int/report/sudan/sudan-au-welcomes-inauguration-darfur-transitional-authority</ref>''' <ref>https://rwandinfo.com/fr/rwanda-la-ministre-rwandaise-monique-mukaruliza-annonce-ladhesion-du-sud-soudan-a-la-communaute-est-africaine/</ref> Yagize kandi uruhare mu ishingwa n’ivugurura ryakurikiyeho mu kigo  [[Ikigo gishinzwe Imisoro n'Amahoro mu Rwanda|gishinzwe Imisoro n'Amahoro mu Rwanda]] igihe yakoraga nka komiseri ushinzwe ubuziranenge (Ubugenzuzi bw’imbere mu Gihugu). Afite ubunararibonye muri serivisi za banki kuko yabaye Komiseri ushinzwe imisoro yo mu Gihugu, Ushinzwe gusesengura imari muri [[Banki ya Kigali]] hagati ya 1998 na 2001. <ref>https://en.igihe.com/news/new-kigali-mayor-briefs</ref>

